node.title: Two men escape serious injury after light plane crashes into ocean off Perth
node.alt: Police and a lifesaver on the beach where a light plane crashed. The wreckage is in the ocean in the background.
node.description: Two men escape serious injury after a light plane crashes into the ocean off a popular Perth beach.
node.content: ["Two men have escaped serious injury after a light plane crashed into the ocean off a popular Perth beach.", "Police responded to calls of a light plane ditching into the ocean off City Beach about 3:30pm on Saturday.", "The pilot\u00a0reported engine troubles before the crash.", "Police said\u00a0the pilot and his male passenger got out of the aircraft and made it back to shore.", "Both have minor injuries."]
